  validation, fixed multiple bugs in PDF generation (correcting NaN values,
  including minutes in calculations, allowing null for number inputs, wiring up
  a download button, and replacing a hardcoded user name), and added regex
  validation for time fields in the Zod schema. The entire process was verified
  with local lint and build checks, culminating in a successful push to the
  remote repository.
